    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable, fully operational driver for anyone looking for a solid foundation. While the engine and transmission function as they should, the car shows its age with some cosmetic imperfections, including minor paint fading on the hood and some wear on the interior upholstery. It has been regularly maintained, though a few minor mechanical updates, such as aging suspension bushings, will eventually need attention. This is an honest car for someone who appreciates a functional vehicle that still has plenty of life left with a little bit of care.",
