    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of uncompromising quality. This vehicle remains in a state of meticulous preservation, exhibiting a flawless exterior profile and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Every aspect of this motorcar has been curated to meet the standards of the most exacting collector. We invite you to experience a vehicle that stands as a benchmark for its class, offering both peerless aesthetic appeal and mechanical precision.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
